article_title: Gallery: MN Orchestra in Old Havana May 16
article_text:
Local

"This appears to be an innocent victim — someone who was in the wrong place at the wrong time," a police spokesman said.

og.description: The Minnesota Orchestra wrapped up its tour of Cuba Saturday evening with some music a the Cafe Havana before having to fly home Sunday.
